::KitKat/GoldenEye::

GoldenEye::

She set Dollen on the ground next to Drillbit and Bludgeon.  She then 
landed and transformed into bot mode and looked at KitKat and 
Drillbit, "WIll she be ok?"


KitKat::
She looked up at Bludgeon and then to Drillbit.  She tried to stand 
agian and made to all fours.  Her legs wobbled but she stood there.
"Let's get everyone round up and scout around for another base. We 
will need it to survive.  I will need someone to go back to the old 
base and scout around for anything salvagable.  We then need to use 
what's left of Phobia's ship to....*she then collapsed as her legs 
gave out.  She lay on the ground breathing heavily and catching her 
breath.  "Phobia." She then realized he hadn't jumpe ship yet. The 
thought of loosing another team member made her spark sink.  "Someone 
get him out of that ship before it explodes."  She then layed her 
head down on the ground and tried to catch her breath.  Her felt her 
body want to give out, but her mind and spark wasn't about to quit 
yet.
